    {
      "title": "陶哲轩最新论文:拒绝技术至上,AI 需要以人为本被重新定义",
      "link": "https://so.html5.qq.com/page/real/search_news?docid=70000021_83969cbad0f15752",
      "snippet": "<p>昨天,陶哲轩在他的个人博客上发布了一则论文更新｡他在贴文中写道,“我很少写哲学性质的长篇文章,上一次大概是 2007 年｡”这位菲尔兹奖得主､加州大学洛杉矶分校数学教授,刚在 arXiv 上传了一篇题为《人工智能时代的数学方法与人类思维》(Mathematical Methods And Human Thoughts In The Age Of AI) ",
      "date": "2026-03-31 19:16:32"
    },
    {
      "title": "[2206.09955] The Sparse-Grid-Based Adaptive Spectral Koopman Method",
      "link": "https://arxiv.org/abs/2206.09955",
      "snippet": "View a PDF of the paper titled The Sparse-Grid-Based Adaptive Spectral Koopman Method, by Bian Li and 2 other authors View PDF Abstract: The adaptive spectral Koopman (ASK) method was introduced to numerically solve autonomous dynamical systems that lay the foundation of numerous applications across different fields in science and engineering. Although ASK achieves high accuracy, it is computationally more expensive for multi-dimensional systems compared with conventional time integration schemes like Runge-Kutta. In this work, we combine the sparse grid and ASK to accelerate the computation for multi-dimensional systems. This sparse-grid-based ASK (SASK) method uses the Smolyak structure to construct multi-dimensional collocation points as well as associated polynomials that are used to approximate eigenfunctions of the Koopman operator of the system. In this way, the number of collocation points is reduced compared with using the tensor product rule. We demonstrate that SASK can be u",
      "date": "2022-06-20 18:31:57"
    },
    {
      "title": "AlphaXiv:aXiv论文开放论坛",
      "link": "https://www.jiaojianli.com/19617.html",
      "snippet": "arXiv始于1991年8月14日｡ arXiv是一个收集物理学､数学､计算机科学与生物学的论文预印本的网站,是如今国际上最权威的预印本平台｡ 当时,为了防止自己的idea在论文被收录前被别人剽窃,人们会将预印稿上传到arvix作为预收录,因此,这就是个可以证明论文原创性(上传时间戳)的文档收录网站｡ ",
      "date": "2024-09-08 03:00:38"
    },
    {
      "title": "【CS-part1】New submissions for Mon, 21 Aug 23 · Issue #534 · Yukeaaa/arxiv-daily · GitHub",
      "link": "https://github.com/Yukeaaa/arxiv-daily/issues/534",
      "snippet": "Keyword: volume render MonoNeRD: NeRF-like Representations for Monocular 3D Object Detection Authors: Junkai Xu, Liang Peng, Haoran Cheng, Hao Li, Wei Qian, Ke Li, Wenxiao Wang, Deng Cai Subjects: Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV) Abstract In the field of monocular 3D detection, it is common practice to utilize scene geometric clues to enhance the detector's performance. However, many existing works adopt these clues explicitly such as estimating a depth map and back-projecting it into 3D space. This explicit methodology induces sparsity in 3D representations due to the increased dimensionalihe KITTI-3D benchmark and Waymo Open Dataset demonstrate the effectiveness of MonoNeRD. Codes are available at https://github.com/cskkxjk/MonoNeRD . Keyword: volumetric render There is no result Keyword: remote render There is no result Keyword: his no result Keyword: medical imaging Learning to In-paint: Domain Adaptive Shape Completion for 3D Organ Segmentation Authors: Mingjin Chen",
      "date": "2023-08-21 07:23:14"
    },
    {
      "title": "国内arxiv镜像网站:让你快速下载论文_arxiv论文网站-CSDN博客",
      "link": "https://blog.csdn.net/mrjkzhangma/article/details/102651213",
      "snippet": "Cornell University 建立了一个论文数据库: https://arxiv.org/ 目前,国外计算机领域的论文基本会第一时间上传至该网站,但是由于该网站在国外,国内在该网站下载论文时会显得比较慢｡因此,国内的开发人员建立了一个国内镜像网站,通过该网站,我们可以快速有效的下载我们所需要的文章｡ 该镜像网站为:http://xxx.itp.ac.cn 下面,我为大家演示一遍如何操作: ",
      "date": "2019-10-20 17:43:24"
    },
    {
      "title": "arXiv被AI水文淹没,新规要求AI生成论文需过同行评审",
      "link": "https://so.html5.qq.com/page/real/search_news?docid=70000021_8176906fcbb96952",
      "snippet": "<p>当地时间 10 月 31 日,由于涌入预印本平台 arXiv 的计算机科学(CS,Compute Science)的由 AI 生成或 AI 辅助生成的综述论文和立场论文数量变得难以管理,<strong>arXiv 更新了关于综述论文和立场论文的审核规则,要求这两类论文必须被期刊或会议接收并完成同行评审之后才能提交到 arXiv 的 CS 类别｡",
      "date": "2025-11-02 14:39:56"
    },
    {
      "title": "arxiv官网,论文预印本网站,收集物理学,数学,计算机科学与生物学等,防剽窃非猪ai导航",
